{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_015CyzCvTyFJQmCZV3KZo5Ks","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→#\n     2→# Copyright (c), Eclipse Foundation, Inc. and its licensors.\n     3→#\n     4→# All rights reserved.\n     5→#\n     6→# This program and the accompanying materials are made available under the\n     7→# terms of the Eclipse Distribution License v1.0, which is available at\n     8→# https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php\n     9→#\n    10→# SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause\n    11→#\n    12→\n    13→PersistenceErrorOccured=A persistence error occurred.\n    14→Previous=Previous\n    15→Next=Next\n    16→\n    17→ContactCreated=Contact was successfully created.\n    18→ContactUpdated=Contact was successfully updated.\n    19→ContactDeleted=Contact was successfully deleted.\n    20→CreateContactTitle=Create New Contact\n    21→CreateContactSaveLink=Save\n    22→CreateContactShowAllLink=Show All Contact Items\n    23→CreateContactIndexLink=Index\n    24→CreateContactLabel_birthday=Birthday:\n    25→CreateContactTitle_birthday=Birthday\n    26→CreateContactLabel_homePhone=Home Phone:\n    27→CreateContactTitle_homePhone=Home Phone\n    28→CreateContactLabel_mobilePhone=Mobile Phone:\n    29→CreateContactTitle_mobilePhone=Mobile Phone\n    30→CreateContactLabel_email=Email:\n    31→CreateContactTitle_email=Email\n    32→CreateContactLabel_lastName=Last Name:\n    33→CreateContactTitle_lastName=Last Name\n    34→CreateContactLabel_firstName=First Name:\n    35→CreateContactTitle_firstName=First Name\n    36→CreateContactLabel_id=Id:\n    37→CreateContactTitle_id=Id\n    38→EditContactTitle=Edit Contact\n    39→EditContactSaveLink=Save\n    40→EditContactViewLink=View\n    41→EditContactShowAllLink=Show All Contact Items\n    42→EditContactIndexLink=Index\n    43→EditContactLabel_birthday=Birthday:\n    44→EditContactTitle_birthday=Birthday\n    45→EditContactLabel_homePhone=Home Phone:\n    46→EditContact